 211.30 

Criteria for evaluating the U.S. operations of foreign banks not subject to consolidated supervision. 



(a) 

General. 

Pursuant to the Foreign Bank Supervision Enhancement Act, Public Law 102-242, 105 Stat. 2286 (1991), (the FBSEA)
