<SUMMARY>
SUMMARY:

 The Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA) announces an informal public meeting to provide an opportunity
for oral and written presentations regarding specific issues raised through the reopening of the Shipyard Employment
Personal Protection Equipment (PPE) rulemaking record (59 FR 34586, July 6, 1994) and the incorporation of the general
industry PPE rulemaking docket (S-060).



